    <details><summary>Should I shut off the water before calling?</summary><p>If water is actively leaking, shut off the nearest fixture valve or the main water shutoff if it is safe to do so. If water is near electrical equipment, avoid touching the area and call for help right away.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Which Brampton neighbourhoods do you serve?</summary><p>Fateh serves Brampton areas including Bramalea, Springdale, Castlemore, Mount Pleasant, Heart Lake, Fletcher's Meadow, Credit Valley, Peel Village, Downtown Brampton, and nearby communities.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Do you handle residential and commercial plumbing?</summary><p>Yes. Fateh helps homeowners, landlords, restaurants, retail units, property managers, and small businesses with plumbing repairs, emergency calls, maintenance issues, and service planning.</p></details>
  </section>

